However, in view of this approach by mobile telephone providers, the absolute disinterest of the Czech regulatory authorities is amazed.
It is not only the position of the ČTU, which, unfortunately, has no power to intervene in economic competition in Czech countries - unlike the United Kingdom and other highly developed countries.
